    <item>
      <title>美国寻求限制中国获取美国人的个人数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/us-data-security-order-to-limit-china-s-access-to-americans-personal-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统将签署一项行政命令，旨在阻止外国实体获取大量美国人的个人数据，因为担心这些数据可能被利用以获得商业和军事优势，特别是被中国和俄罗斯利用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/us-data-security-order-to-limit-china-s-access-to-americans-personal-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>发言人称纳瓦尔尼的葬礼将于周五在莫斯科举行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/navalny-s-funeral-to-be-held-friday-in-moscow-spokeswoman-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的发言人表示，本月早些时候在监狱中去世的俄罗斯反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼将于周五在莫斯科下葬，此前他曾指责当局试图干扰这位活动人士的葬礼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/navalny-s-funeral-to-be-held-friday-in-moscow-spokeswoman-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:58:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国一半地方议会担心未来几年破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/half-of-uk-local-councils-fear-bankruptcy-in-coming-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对高级议会人士的调查发现，英国市政厅正计划削减公园、休闲和艺术方面的资金，超过一半的市政厅预计在未来几年破产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/half-of-uk-local-councils-fear-bankruptcy-in-coming-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:44:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚间谍头子称外国政权招募了前议员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/australian-spy-chief-says-foreign-regime-recruited-ex-lawmaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚国内间谍头子透露，外国政权招募了一名前议员，作为通过高级人物（包括总理家庭成员）获取机密信息的计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/australian-spy-chief-says-foreign-regime-recruited-ex-lawmaker</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管大幅加息，尼日利亚奈拉仍创历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/nigeria-s-naira-usd-ngn-drops-to-fresh-record-low-despite-jumbo-rate-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚的大幅加息未能阻止奈拉的下跌，这个西非国家的货币在官方市场上兑美元汇率跌至新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/nigeria-s-naira-usd-ngn-drops-to-fresh-record-low-despite-jumbo-rate-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:45:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和菲律宾加强经济联系以抵御中国风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/us-philippines-to-bolster-economic-ties-to-fend-off-china-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马尼拉驻华盛顿特使表示，在中国利用其经济影响力进行“胁迫”的风险下，美国和菲律宾正在努力建立更紧密的贸易和投资关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/us-philippines-to-bolster-economic-ties-to-fend-off-china-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:39:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陷入困境的日本首相志愿者将出席道德委员会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/embattled-japan-pm-volunteers-to-appear-before-ethics-panel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄将出席议会道德委员会，试图扭转执政党行贿丑闻的新一页，该丑闻在领导层投票前几个月削弱了他的支持率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/embattled-japan-pm-volunteers-to-appear-before-ethics-panel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冯德莱恩警告欧洲必须加强威胁防御</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/europe-needs-to-ramp-up-defenses-to-threats-von-der-leyen-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席乌苏拉·冯德莱恩表示，乌克兰盟友应考虑利用俄罗斯冻结资产的利润为基辅购买武器，并警告欧洲必须为更广泛战争的风险做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/europe-needs-to-ramp-up-defenses-to-threats-von-der-leyen-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:29:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称马来西亚法院恢复前总理穆希丁的贪污指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/malaysian-court-reinstates-ex-pm-muhyiddin-s-graft-charges-star</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《星报》报道，马来西亚上诉法院恢复了前总理穆希丁·亚辛的四项滥用职权指控，这对这位反对派领导人构成了新的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/malaysian-court-reinstates-ex-pm-muhyiddin-s-graft-charges-star</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 07:57:34 GMT</pubDate>
